T.query: select e.emp_no  as emp_no ,s.salary,e.first_name,e.last_name,e.birth_date,e.hire_date,s.from_date,d.dept_no from employees e join salaries s on e.emp_no = s.emp_no join titles t on e.emp_no = t.emp_no and t.from_date = s.from_date join dept_emp de on de.emp_no = e.emp_no join departments d on de.dept_no = d.dept_no where e.emp_no > 495500 or t.from_date = '1996-01-01' or de.from_date = '1996-01-01' or e.last_name like 'Alb%' or d.dept_no ='d002' or s.salary > 91000 or t.title='Manager' or e.birth_date = '1965-01-01' or s.to_date = '1996-01-01' or t.to_date = '1997-01-01';
